{CALCULATE MAS USING PARAMETERS P1 AND P2}
MA1:=MA(CLOSE, P1);
MA2:=MA(CLOSE, P2);

{1. FILL BACKGROUND FIRST (DARKER COLORS TO PREVENT COVERING CANDLES)}
FILLRGN(MA1, MA2, MA1 > MA2), COLOR320000;  {BULLISH CLOUD}
FILLRGN(MA1, MA2, MA1 < MA2), COLOR003200;  {BEARISH CLOUD}

{2. DRAW THE ACTUAL LINES ON TOP}
LINE1:MA1, COLORWHITE;
LINE2:MA2, COLORYELLOW;